mil.nga.giat.geowave.ingest.hdfs

Interface StageToHdfsPlugin<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type for intermediate data, it must match the type supported by the Avro schema
    All Superinterfaces:
    HdfsPluginBase, LocalPluginBase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractStageFileToHdfs, GeoLifeIngestPlugin, GpxIngestPlugin, TdriveIngestPlugin

    public interface StageToHdfsPlugin<T>
extends HdfsPluginBase, LocalPluginBase
    This is the main plugin interface for reading from a local file system, and staging intermediate data to HDFS from any file that is supported.

    • Method Summary
